        <para> Tamboti is a flexible metadata framework that allows you to search for existing records and enter new ones. </para>
        <para> You can grant access to your records to other people, for example display or editing access, 
            or restrict any use of your records to just you. </para>
        <para> For entering new records, templates have been made with instructions on best practices. 
            You can ask the HRA to create templates adapted to project-specific needs.
        </para>
        <para> Note that the interface is constantly updated and may change in structure or appearance. </para>
